          "Fund Transfer"
        ],
        "summary": "Initiate a fund transfer",
        "description": "This operation allows a user to initiate a transfer of funds from one account to another. It requires specifying the source account, destination account, and the amount to be transferred. Upon successful completion, the funds will be moved accordingly.",
